              <path d="M93.9676 39.0409C96.393 38.4038 97.8624 35.9116 97.0079 33.5539C95.2932 28.8227 92.871 24.3692 89.8167 20.348C85.8452 15.1192 80.8826 10.7238 75.2124 7.41289C69.5422 4.10194 63.2754 1.94025 56.7698 1.05124C51.7666 0.367541 46.6976 0.446843 41.7345 1.27873C39.2613 1.69328 37.813 4.19778 38.4501 6.62326C39.0873 9.04874 41.5694 10.4717 44.0505 10.1071C47.8511 9.54855 51.7191 9.52689 55.5402 10.0491C60.8642 10.7766 65.9928 12.5457 70.6331 15.2552C75.2735 17.9648 79.3347 21.5619 82.5849 25.841C84.9175 28.9121 86.7997 32.2913 88.1811 35.8758C89.083 38.2158 91.5421 39.6781 93.9676 39.0409Z" fill="currentFill" />
            </svg>
            <span class="sr-only">Loading...</span>
          </div>
        </button>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-y-4 gap-x-2 items-center mt-12">

          {% for block in section.blocks %}
            {% case block.type %}
              {% when 'feature' %}
                <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                  <img
                    class="w-8 h-8"
                    src="{{ block.settings.image | image_url: width: 64, height: 64 }}"
                    alt="{{ block.settings.title }}"
                    width="32"
                    height="32"
                    loading="lazy">
                  <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">{{ block.settings.title }}</p>
                </div>
            {% endcase %}
          {% endfor %}
          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-replay-30-100.svg?v=1737552710"
              alt="Free 30-day returns"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">Free 30-day returns</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-shield-100.svg?v=1737552800"
              alt="100% Satisfaction guarantee"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">100% Satisfaction guarantee</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-percentage.svg?v=1737553256"
              alt="60% to 85% cheaper"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">60% to 85% cheaper</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-diamond-100.svg?v=1737552836"
              alt="High-quality"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">High-quality</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-time_2.svg?v=1737553604"
              alt="Long-lasting"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">Long-lasting</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <img
              class="w-8 h-8"
              src="//dialectfragrances.com/cdn/shop/files/icons8-leaf-100.svg?v=1737553281"
              alt="Vegan, Cruelty Free & Carbon Neutral"
              width="32"
              height="32"
              loading="lazy">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs leading-4">Vegan, Cruelty Free &amp; Carbon Neutral</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-4 md:p-8" x-data="{
                activeAccordion: 0,
                toggleAccordion(index) {
                    this.activeAccordion = this.activeAccordion === index ? null : index;
                },
                isActive(index) {
                    return this.activeAccordion === index;
                }
            }">
          <div class="space-y-4">


            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" :class="{ 'shadow-md': isActive(0) }">
              <button
                @click="toggleAccordion(0)"
                class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                :class="{ 'rounded-b-none': isActive(0) }">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">How do I apply Orphic?</span>
                <span class="text-3xl font-light transition-transform duration-300 transform" :class="{ 'rotate-45': isActive(0) }">+</span>
              </button>
              <div
                x-show="isActive(0)"
                x-collapse
                x-cloak
                class="px-6 pb-5 pt-0 text-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <p>Apply Orphic to pulse points such as wrists, neck, and behind the ears. Start with 1-2 sprays and adjust based on your preference. The fragrance will develop over time.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" :class="{ 'shadow-md': isActive(1) }">
              <button
                @click="toggleAccordion(1)"
                class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                :class="{ 'rounded-b-none': isActive(1) }">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">How long does the fragrance last?</span>
                <span class="text-3xl font-light transition-transform duration-300 transform" :class="{ 'rotate-45': isActive(1) }">+</span>
              </button>
              <div
                x-show="isActive(1)"
                x-collapse
                x-cloak
                class="px-6 pb-5 pt-0 text-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <p>Orphic is designed to be long-lasting, typically lasting 8-10 hours on the skin. The fragrance may vary slightly depending on your skin type and environment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" :class="{ 'shadow-md': isActive(2) }">
              <button
                @click="toggleAccordion(2)"
                class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                :class="{ 'rounded-b-none': isActive(2) }">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">Is Orphic suitable for sensitive skin?</span>
                <span class="text-3xl font-light transition-transform duration-300 transform" :class="{ 'rotate-45': isActive(2) }">+</span>
              </button>
              <div
                x-show="isActive(2)"
                x-collapse
                x-cloak
                class="px-6 pb-5 pt-0 text-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <p>Yes, Orphic is formulated to be gentle on all skin types. However, if you have particularly sensitive skin, we recommend doing a patch test before full application.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out" :class="{ 'shadow-md': isActive(3) }">
              <button
                @click="toggleAccordion(3)"
                class="w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300"
                :class="{ 'rounded-b-none': isActive(3) }">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold">What are the key notes in Orphic?</span>
                <span class="text-3xl font-light transition-transform duration-300 transform" :class="{ 'rotate-45': isActive(3) }">+</span>
              </button>
              <div
                x-show="isActive(3)"
                x-collapse
                x-cloak
                class="px-6 pb-5 pt-0 text-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
                <p>Orphic features top notes of bergamot and lemon, a heart of lavender and rosemary, with a base of vetiver and patchouli, creating a sophisticated and long-lasting fragrance.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
